pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: index.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: Amal Rekik
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  toc: true
  toc-depth: 4
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  theme:
    light:
      - yeti
      - assets/styling/styles.scss
    dark:
      - darkly
      - assets/styling/styles_dark.scss
  pagetitle: 'Amal Rekik | {{< meta title >}}'
  smooth-scroll: true
  code-block-bg: false
  title: ''
  subtitle: ''
  about:
    template: solana
    image-width: 12em
    id: hero-heading
    links:
      - icon: github
        aria-label: Github
        href: 'https://github.com/Rekik-Amal'
      - icon: linkedin
        aria-label: www.linkedin.com/in/amal-rekik-88a655252
      - icon: send
        text: Email
        href: amal.rekik33@gmail.com
  page-layout: full
  header-includes:
    - |
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/index.css">
  resources:
    - assets/index.css
